snippet.title: Jumpaï Alpha 0.5 Trailer - Race with your friends on levels you created! (Jumpai)
snippet.description:
Download Jumpaï : https://frame-perfect.itch.io/jumpai

Jumpaï is an online multiplayer platformer where players build their own levels to compete on them! Ever wanted to race your friends on a  level you made? This is your chance!

You can also sit back and relax in your hub. Invite some friends and have a chat.

You can watch your replay or anyone else's on the leaderboard! You can even export it!

Website: http://jumpai.net/
Twitter : https://twitter.com/jumpaigame
Discord : https://discord.gg/Guv4UYn

Some music used in this trailer is property of CodeManu on https://opengameart.org/content/platformer-game-music-pack
